[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/20910634","html_url":"https://github.com/glfw/glfw/issues/93#issuecomment-20910634","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/93","id":20910634,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDIwOTEwNjM0","user":{"login":"dmitshur","id":1924134,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjQxMzQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1924134?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur","html_url":"https://github.com/dmitshur","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-07-12T23:56:14Z","updated_at":"2013-07-30T16:59:07Z","body":"For OS X, in `cocoa_window.m`,\n1. Comment out `SetFrontProcess(&psn);` This makes the window not take focus when created.\n2. Add `[window->ns.object setLevel:NSFloatingWindowLevel];` somewhere in `createWindow()`, for example after `[window->ns.object center];`. This makes the window hover above all other windows even when not active.\n\nPersonally, I'd love two window creation flags that control this to be added to GLFW, because they can be useful when developing OpenGL apps. (I've created it as issue #101).\n","author_association":"COLLABORATOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/20910634/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"dmitshur","id":1924134,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjQxMzQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1924134?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur","html_url":"https://github.com/dmitshur","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmitshur/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/20912771","html_url":"https://github.com/glfw/glfw/issues/93#issuecomment-20912771","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/93","id":20912771,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDIwOTEyNzcx","user":{"login":"smcguffee","id":5000332,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUwMDAzMzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5000332?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee","html_url":"https://github.com/smcguffee","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-07-13T01:45:32Z","updated_at":"2013-07-30T13:41:51Z","body":"Hi, shurcooL,\n\nThanks for the quick reply! It worked great!\n\nIn the end I changed three functions in cocoa_window.m:\n\n```\nstatic GLboolean initializeAppKit(const _GLFWwndconfig* wndconfig) //Note I pass in an argument now, it was taking void\n{\n    if (NSApp)\n        return GL_TRUE;\n    [GLFWApplication sharedApplication];\n    ProcessSerialNumber psn = {0, kCurrentProcess};\n    TransformProcessType(&psn, kProcessTransformToForegroundApplication);\n    bool theWindowIsVisible = true;                                             //check if the window is hidden, !visible       \n    if (wndconfig != NULL)                                                      //if possible \n    {                                                                           //\n        if (!wndconfig->visible)                                                //if not visible\n        {                                                                       //\n            theWindowIsVisible = false;                                         //take note\n        }                                                                       //\n    }                                                                           //\n    if (theWindowIsVisible)                                                     //\n    {                                                                           //\n        SetFrontProcess(&psn);                                                  //only set front process if the window is visible\n    }\n#if defined(_GLFW_USE_MENUBAR)\n        createMenuBar();\n#endif\n        [NSApp finishLaunching];\n        return GL_TRUE;\n    }\n\n\nint _glfwPlatformCreateWindow(_GLFWwindow* window,\n        const _GLFWwndconfig* wndconfig,\n        const _GLFWfbconfig* fbconfig)\n{\n    if (!initializeAppKit(wndconfig))                                           //pass in the window configuration\n        return GL_FALSE;\n    if (_glfw.ns.delegate == nil)\n    {\n        _glfw.ns.delegate = [[GLFWApplicationDelegate alloc] init];\n        if (_glfw.ns.delegate == nil)\n        {\n            _glfwInputError(GLFW_PLATFORM_ERROR,\n                    \"Cocoa: Failed to create application delegate\");\n            return GL_FALSE;\n        }\n        [NSApp setDelegate : _glfw.ns.delegate];\n    }\n    window->ns.delegate = [[GLFWWindowDelegate alloc] initWithGlfwWindow : window];\n    if (window->ns.delegate == nil)\n    {\n        _glfwInputError(GLFW_PLATFORM_ERROR,\n                \"Cocoa: Failed to create window delegate\");\n        return GL_FALSE;\n    }\n    if (!createWindow(window, wndconfig))\n        return GL_FALSE;\n    if (!_glfwCreateContext(window, wndconfig, fbconfig))\n        return GL_FALSE;\n    [window->nsgl.context setView : window->ns.view];\n    if (wndconfig->monitor)\n        enterFullscreenMode(window);\n    return GL_TRUE;\n}\n\n\nstatic GLboolean createWindow(_GLFWwindow* window,\n        const _GLFWwndconfig* wndconfig)\n{\n    unsigned int styleMask = 0;\n\n    if (wndconfig->monitor || !wndconfig->decorated)\n        styleMask = NSBorderlessWindowMask;\n    else\n    {\n        styleMask = NSTitledWindowMask | NSClosableWindowMask |\n                NSMiniaturizableWindowMask;\n\n        if (wndconfig->resizable)\n            styleMask |= NSResizableWindowMask;\n    }\n    window->ns.object = [[GLFWWindow alloc]\n            initWithContentRect : NSMakeRect(0, 0, wndconfig->width, wndconfig->height)\n            styleMask : styleMask\n            backing : NSBackingStoreBuffered\n            defer : NO];\n    if (window->ns.object == nil)\n    {\n        _glfwInputError(GLFW_PLATFORM_ERROR, \"Cocoa: Failed to create window\");\n        return GL_FALSE;\n    }\n    window->ns.view = [[GLFWContentView alloc] initWithGlfwWindow : window];\n    if ([window->ns.view respondsToSelector : @selector(setWantsBestResolutionOpenGLSurface :)])\n        [window->ns.view setWantsBestResolutionOpenGLSurface : YES];\n    [window->ns.object setTitle : [NSString stringWithUTF8String : wndconfig->title]];\n    [window->ns.object setContentView : window->ns.view];\n    [window->ns.object setDelegate : window->ns.delegate];\n    [window->ns.object setAcceptsMouseMovedEvents : YES];\n    [window->ns.object disableCursorRects];\n    [window->ns.object center];\n    if (wndconfig != NULL)\n    {\n        if (!wndconfig->visible)\n        {\n            [window->ns.object setLevel : NSFloatingWindowLevel];\n        }\n    }\n    if ([window->ns.object respondsToSelector : @selector(setRestorable :)])\n        [window->ns.object setRestorable : NO];\n    return GL_TRUE;\n}\n```\n","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/20912771/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"smcguffee","id":5000332,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUwMDAzMzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5000332?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee","html_url":"https://github.com/smcguffee","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/smcguffee/repos","ev